Package: welcome-art
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: figlet, lolcat, bash (>= 4.0)
Recommends: git, wget, unzip
Maintainer: Welcome-Art Team <support@welcome-art.org>
Description: Dynamic figlet art with gradient effects for SSH/VPS login
 Welcome-Art is a comprehensive modular bash script package that displays
 dynamic figlet art with gradient effects and customizable text upon
 SSH/VPS login. It provides a beautiful and informative welcome screen
 for Ubuntu 18+ systems.
 .
 Features:
  * Dynamic figlet art rendering with lolcat gradient effects
  * Modular template system with customizable art styles
  * System-wide and user-level configuration support
  * Automatic execution on SSH login
  * Template management and updates
  * 256-color terminal support
  * Comprehensive logging and error handling
 .
 The package includes:
  * Main executable (/usr/local/bin/welcome-art)
  * Configuration files (/etc/welcome-art/config)
  * Art template storage (/etc/welcome-art/art/)
  * Subcommand modules (/etc/welcome-art/scripts/)
  * Auto-execution trigger (/etc/profile.d/welcome-art.sh)
Homepage: https://github.com/welcome-art/welcome-art
Bugs: https://github.com/welcome-art/welcome-art/issues